 R←Test_Config_001(stopFlag batchFlag);⎕TRAP;projectPath;ref;projectName;result;list
⍝ Create a project and check whether `acre.config[CaseCode]` is honored.
 ⎕TRAP←(999 'C' '. ⍝ Deliberate error')(0 'N')

 R←∆Failed

 projectName←⊃⎕SI
 projectPath←∆PATH,'/',projectName
 #.⎕SHADOW projectName
 ref←⍎projectName #.⎕NS''
 ref.⎕FX'r←Hello' 'r←''World'''
 ∆ClearLog

 :Trap (~stopFlag)/0
     result←∆RunUcmd'Createproject ',projectPath,' #.',projectName,' -casecode=on'
 :Else
     →GoToTidyUp 1
 :EndTrap
 →GoToTidyUp result≢'#.',projectName
 →GoToTidyUp 1≠F.IsFile projectPath,'\APLSource\Hello-1.aplf'
 F.RmDir projectPath
 ∆RunUcmd'Close #.',projectName


 :Trap (~stopFlag)/0
     result←∆RunUcmd'Createproject ',projectPath,' #.',projectName,' -casecode=off'
 :Else
     →GoToTidyUp 1
 :EndTrap
 →GoToTidyUp result≢'#.',projectName
 →GoToTidyUp 1≠F.IsFile projectPath,'\APLSource\Hello.aplf'
 F.RmDir projectPath
 ∆RunUcmd'Close #.',projectName

 :Trap (~stopFlag)/0
     result←∆RunUcmd'Createproject ',projectPath,' #.',projectName  ⍝ Default is "off"
 :Else
     →GoToTidyUp 1
 :EndTrap
 →GoToTidyUp result≢'#.',projectName
 →GoToTidyUp 1≠F.IsFile projectPath,'\APLSource\Hello.aplf'
 F.RmDir projectPath

 R←∆OK

∆TidyUp:
 F.RmDir projectPath
 ∆ClearLog
 ∆RunUcmd'Close #.',projectName
⍝Done
